{"tid":1512733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心藍絲隱性文宣","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T06:58:30.000Z","uid":3634,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f95b26c7c91535ae8653c78444838b2990f1c105","tid":1512733,"uid":3634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:11:24.000Z","msg":"近嚟連登有好多 Post 都係有個 Pattern. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「乜乜乜（藍絲）send 咗呢樣嘢俾我，點拆好？」<br />\n然後下加藍絲啲智障/老屈文宣，根本正常巴絲都識拆嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然各位精明嘅巴絲唔會中伏，<br />\n但呢啲 Post 可能令啲近嚟先識連登嘅人(eg 銀髮族)困惑 。<br />\n<br />\n我極度懷疑呢啲係藍絲嘅隱性文宣，有以下用途:<br />\n1. 引起圍屌，令垃圾堆上熱門，阻礙其他討論<br />\n2. 浪費各位巴絲可以用嚟進行有意義討論嘅時間<br />\n3. 動搖心態未夠穩嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我強烈建議大家千祈唔好推嗰啲垃圾 Post！要回都用不推文回覆！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0323e967fc974e81e687ecf8a4a1ee410ddbb44c","tid":1512733,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=94b65886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=fdb60d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=0ab6e0ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"7ccb0f21